allocation[r], activeNeed[r])<br/><br/>STEP 5: Combine Tiers & Apply Policy<br/>  - final_allocation[r] = tier1_allocation[r] + tier2_allocation[r]<br/>  - offer[r] = final_allocation[r] × commitment_rate<br/><br/>STEP 6: Publish with ITC Stamp<br/>  - Event++: stamp.event += 1<br/>  - PUBLISH: {offer_id, itc_stamp, offers: [(r, offer[r], tier)]}
